<div class="story">
  <p>Monteray Shores is a sound front community in Corolla situated on the Currituck Sound. There is an active home owners association which maintains the private roads, the club house, the community, 4 tennis courts and a sound access. You will find Monteray Shores just before the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/corolla-light.asp" title="Corolla Light">Corolla Light</a> and west of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/corolla/whalehead.asp" title="Whalehead Beach">Whalehead Beach</a>. </p>
